{
  "texts": [
    "This work may be used to enhance the physical plausibility and controllability of video generation models.",
    "Applications include video content creation with fine-grained output control for physicsbased forces and second-order solutions that leverage enhanced intuitive physics such as motion planning and world simulation.",
    "We urge the community to think critically about the potential risks of our work, specifically in the modeling of physical phenomena.",
    "Our work is not a substitute for precise physical simulation, rather we focus on what we have described as \"intuitive physics\", i.e.",
    "motion that is visually plausible to humans."
  ]
}